%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor JIRA_SYS as JIRA System

participant ADP as Service Adapter
participant ORCH@{ "type":"boundary", "alias":"Journey Orchestrator"}
participant JIRA as JIRA Sync Service
participant PRIMARYDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant READDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant KAFKA@{ "type": "queue", "alias": "Message Bus"}

participant AI_ORCH as AI Orchestrator
participant EMB as Embedding Service
participant VECTORDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}

JIRA_SYS->>ADP: Webhook (Issue Update)
ADP->>ORCH: Forward payload
ORCH->>JIRA: Process webhook

JIRA->>PRIMARYDB: Persist JIRA WBS update
PRIMARYDB-->>JIRA: Success

Note over PRIMARYDB,READDB: Async replication
PRIMARYDB-->>READDB: Sync data

ORCH->>KAFKA: Publish JiraWBSSynced Event

%% ---- AI Pipeline (ASYNC) ----

KAFKA-->>AI_ORCH: Consume event

AI_ORCH->>PRIMARYDB: Fetch updated JIRA data
PRIMARYDB-->>AI_ORCH: Data

AI_ORCH->>EMB: Generate embeddings (chunking)
EMB-->>AI_ORCH: Vector embeddings

AI_ORCH->>VECTORDB: Store embeddings
VECTORDB-->>AI_ORCH: Stored

Note over VECTORDB: Ready for RAG / semantic search